description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Band 6 Speech and Language Therapist to join our Bank Staff to work with children and young people and families in a variety of locations and settings across Shropshire and Telford.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant will join an enthusiastic and friendly team of Children’s Therapists and Assistants. There are systems in place that provide good professional support through clinical training, staff meetings, peer review, supervision, and access to Trust wide leadership training.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be required to provide assessment and intervention for children’s communication and speech and language difficulties in partnership with families and staff, working in Early Years settings, Clinics and Schools and to support the coordination of care in local clinical teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post will include innovative ways of working, including remote delivery of care packages for children and their families.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant will need to be able to meet the travel requirements of the post.  Shropshire is a large rural county.&lt;/p&gt;
